{"tid":251572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(貓義工) 69歲場主被迫遷 400貓狗前路茫茫","createTime":"2017-05-21T05:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T15:45:19.000Z","uid":54574,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"149eadb7e252bcb0e46b748d07b075e7c545b7bb","tid":251572,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/photo/bkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170521121400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170521121400&h=60c63205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/photo/bkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001_02p.jpg?20170521121400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20170521121400&h=38d89b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「每一隻動物都係生命，唔係我哋可以去摧殘，亦都唔係畀我哋去遺棄。」今年69歲的何太將大半生奉獻予流浪貓狗，她成立了「眾生緣流浪動物之家」，在元朗租用一個三萬呎地方照料被人遺棄的毛孩，最高峰時場內有過千隻貓狗。<br />\n<br />\n何太為人低調，不少動物義工只聞其名，偶爾會聽到她拯救流浪貓狗的事跡，而何太亦安於平凡，只想平平淡淡與她的毛孩寶貝結伴終老，但只可惜事與願違。<br />\n<br />\n一直支持動物之家的善長突然去世，龐大營運開支頓時無以為繼，再加上業主最近要求收地，何太與毛孩們必須在年底前搬走。<br />\n<br />\n眼前困局應如何解決？經過義工朋友多番游說，性格內斂的何太終於肯面對鏡頭，道出半世人為動物傾盡心力的點滴，希望可以引起各界關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/bkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170521%2Fbkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=504a449d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170521/bkn-20170521120041896-0521_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3fef9f8da22ec2f64d8c5ba2db8c9d93816a9c35","tid":251572,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"400貓狗迫埋一齊住，算唔算虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7434358e674fbdd49edd8e922b601b3d870b7a","tid":251572,"uid":46241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc015ad26bdfc41a49854760e68eff34088ae5fa","tid":251572,"uid":45684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>400貓狗迫埋一齊住，算唔算虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三萬呎喎，你屋企幾多呎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a48c0e226cac181d5f22f78c44488854c13ddbf","tid":251572,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>400貓狗迫埋一齊住，算唔算虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三萬呎喎，你屋企幾多呎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n30,000/400=75<br />\n好細<br />\n再加上照顧人手係1:400<br />\n環境唔會好得去邊<br />\n仲有計埋400隻動物痾屎有加乘，估計應該好惡劣下"},{"pid":"7c99f2fd685bbc49ba735e88ba43ebdddf21edf8","tid":251572,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"動物唔好生仔<br />\n送上大陸酒樓一晚清曬"},{"pid":"71c0748f7862d343a2d213476d0a4008fa85ae4b","tid":251572,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>400貓狗迫埋一齊住，算唔算虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三萬呎喎，你屋企幾多呎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n30,000/400=75<br />\n好細<br />\n再加上照顧人手係1:400<br />\n環境唔會好得去邊<br />\n仲有計埋400隻動物痾屎有加乘，估計應該好惡劣下</blockquote><br />\n一個人大過隻動物咁多倍，但係生活空間先多3幾十呎，然後話自己環境好過啲動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p